Name: Rock 'n' Roll Dango Milk
Desc: Having sat beneath the stage for a day and a night, this Dango Milk has been fermented using the yeast of Rock 'n' Roll, transforming it into Rock 'n' Roll Dango Milk!\nThey say that its flavor has undergone some marvelous change, but still more amazingly, it can be sold for twice the price of the original version!\nThat really rocks.
Effect: Restores 26% of Max HP to the selected character and regenerates 570 HP every 5s for 30s.
